      "commercial": "Nouaceur is a major industrial/logistics area tied to the airport and multiple industrial parks: A\u00e9ropole de Nouaceur (industrial zone; created 1999; ~100 ha) with address details pointing to Mohammed V Airport area. Industrial-estate.gov.ma (A\u00e9ropole Nouaceur) (https://industrial-estate.gov.ma/fiche-zone.php?lang=fr&id=170&nature_offer=&area=0&area_max=0)\n\nMIDPARC Nouaceur is an operational industrial acceleration zone (created 2013; ~140 ha). ONUDI/Kavaa (MIDPARC) (https://onudi.kavaa.fr/fiche-zone.php?lang=fr&id=221&nature_offer=-1&area=0&area_max=0)\n\nRetail/commercial nearby: La Plaza de Bouskoura (shopping center) in \u201cBouskoura Ville Verte,\u201d with address \u201cAvenue Patrice Lumumba - 27182 Bouskoura Ville Verte.\u201d La Plaza de Bouskoura (https://www.laplazadebouskoura.com)",
      "transport": "Rail: Casablanca \u2194 Nouaceur has ONCF rail service (example itinerary: Gare Oasis to Ennouasser ~22 minutes; schedule/cost details summarized by Rome2Rio). Rome2Rio (Casablanca\u2013Nouaceur) (https://www.rome2rio.com/s/Casablanca/Nouaceur)\n\nBus: Moovit indicates bus line \u201c312\u201d serves Nouacer area in Casablanca region (transit guide listing). Moovit (Nouacer) (https://moovitapp.com/index/en/public_transit-nouacer-Casablanca-site_79884344-5496)\n\nRegional airport proximity: the station is on the Nouaceur axis near Mohammed V International Airport (CMN), and major projects cite proximity to the airport and A1/A3 motorways. Le360 (Nouaceur ZAI) (https://fr.le360.ma/economie/nouaceur-lance-sa-deuxieme-zone-dacceleration-industrielle_NOTUKNVWK5GJ3AZQAL7GSMS4I4/)",
      "additional": "Petrom\u2019s official website has dedicated pages for several \u201cIstiraha\u201d sites (e.g., Istiraha Bouskoura 2), but the \u201cR\u00e9seau\u201d page did not provide an actual station directory or GPS-enabled locator in the fetched content. PETROM \u2013 R\u00e9seau (http://petrom.ma/reseau/)\n\nThe term \u201cVictoria\u201d in this Casablanca/Nouaceur context appears to refer to the Victoria urban development / bypass (\u201cvoie de contournement de Victoria\u201d) around Bouskoura/Ouled Saleh, which is mentioned as an access route for the new Ouled Saleh industrial acceleration zone. Le360 (Nouaceur ZAI) (https://fr.le360.ma/economie/nouaceur-lance-sa-deuxieme-zone-dacceleration-industrielle_NOTUKNVWK5GJ3AZQAL7GSMS4I4/)"
