      "competitors": "Shell station on Route d\u2019El Jadida in Casablanca with published coordinates 33.55795, -7.6441846 (close to Ferme Bretonne corridor) (Maps.me Shell listing (https://maps.me/catalog/transport/amenity-fuel/shell-9223372037445318356/)).\nShell also lists multiple Casablanca stations including one on Route d\u2019El Jadida (no coordinates on listing page) (Shell station locator (https://find.shell.com/ma/fuel/locations/casablanca/en_US)).\nYandex lists a Shell location on Route El Jadida, Casablanca (competitor confirmation) (Yandex Shell (https://yandex.com/maps/org/18429207122/)).",
      "infrastructure": "Casablanca Am\u00e9nagement mobility program between Casablanca and Nouaceur includes major road widenings/new links (e.g., widening RR320 Route d\u2019Azemmour, doubling RN1 segments, new interchanges) with global budget 2 billion MAD (Casa Am\u00e9nagement (https://www.casa-amenagement.ma/fr/nos-projets/infrastructures-de-mobilite-entre-la-prefecture-de-casablanca-et-la-province-de-nouaceur)).\nA separate reported road project aims to ease traffic between Hay Hassani and Dar Bouazza with first phase budget 100 million MAD (target completion Oct 2025) (Yabiladi (https://en.yabiladi.com/articles/details/171571/casablanca-launches-major-road-project.html)).\nMohammed V Airport new terminal project: investment about 15 billion MAD, capacity +20M pax/year, targeted operational 2029 (Airports 2030 strategy) (African Pilot Magazine (https://africanpilot.africa/reveal-of-the-new-terminal-at-mohammed-v-airport/)).",
      "commercial": "The station is in/near Ferme Bretonne on the Route d\u2019El Jadida corridor, an axis connecting Casablanca toward the airport/Nouaceur and retail zones (incl. Marjane areas mentioned as part of the Route d\u2019El Jadida commercial corridor) (Masscom Global (https://www.masscomglobal.com/moroccos-world-class-advertising-sites-now-open-across-most-prestigious-locations-2026/)).\nIndustrial activity is present in Hay Hassani, including Zone industrielle Diar Lissasfa (example distributor address in Lissasfa Hay Hassani) (Mactac Graphics (https://www.mactacgraphics.eu/english/home/find-distributor/maroc-laminage.html)).",
      "transport": "Road access: the site is on Route d\u2019El Jadida, a main southwest axis linking Casablanca toward Nouaceur/Mohammed V Airport and beyond (context from Casablanca\u2013Nouaceur mobility program) (Casa Am\u00e9nagement (https://www.casa-amenagement.ma/fr/nos-projets/infrastructures-de-mobilite-entre-la-prefecture-de-casablanca-et-la-province-de-nouaceur)).\nPublic transport in the broader area is served by Casa Tramway/Casa Busway network (official site for lines/schedules) (CasaTramway (https://www.casatramway.ma)).\nHay Hassani can be reached from Casa Voyageurs by tram + bus (Rome2Rio itinerary referencing CasaTramway) (Rome2Rio (https://www.rome2rio.com/fr/s/Gare-de-Casa-Voyageurs/Hay-Hassani-%E2%B5%83%E2%B4%B0%E2%B5%A2-%E2%B5%8D%E2%B5%83%E2%B4%B0%E2%B5%99%E2%B4%B0%E2%B5%8F%E2%B5%89-%D8%AD%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86%D9%8A)).\nAirport proximity proxy: accommodations in Ferme Bretonne report Mohammed V International Airport about 22 km away (useful distance indicator) (Agoda (https://www.agoda.com/en-sg/residence-b-livin-la-ferme-bretonne/hotel/casablanca-ma.html)).",
      "additional": "Petrom Istiraha Fleche Du Sud listing appears in Casablanca directories with address \u201cRoute El Jadida, Ferme Bretonne\u201d (CityInfo (https://www.city-info.ma/casablanca/fr/org/2375133137/15222/)).\nA Waze listing for \u201cIstiraha Station (Petrole Du Maghreb (Petrom))\u201d gives a different road reference (\u201cRoute Nouaceur\u201d) and a plus code HC49+597, suggesting potential confusion with another Petrom \u201cIstiraha\u201d in Greater Casablanca (Waze (https://www.waze.com/fr/live-map/directions/ma/casablanca-settat/casablanca/istiraha-station-(petrole-du-maghreb-(petrom))?to=place.ChIJH5oXqM8ypg0RqIFp9NgJOk8))."
